730e51e99f57a2a73b023bd167d22ef1c","tid":1808543,"uid":56541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/23723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F23723&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=86f110d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F23723&h=d962b9c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/23723</a><br />\n以前試過一次work<br />\n<br />\n1.首先，你需要先確認自己的 iPhone 還剩下多少空間。打開 iPhone 內的「設定」&gt;「一般」&gt;「儲存空間與 iCloud 用量」。<br />\n2.接下來，打開 iTunes Store，然後隨便找一部大容量的電影（HD 畫質更好）。若以 1080P 畫質為例，通常一部電影的檔案大小約在 4GB 左右。注意，這部電影的容量必須要比你的 iPhone 剩餘的空間還要大，這一點千萬要注意，若是選了容量太小的電影，那就真的開始下載了。你可以在電影的「詳情」內看到所選影片的大小。<br />\n3.選擇「購買」電影。這時候系統會彈出「無法下載。可用儲存空間不足」的訊息。<br />\n4.這時候，可以重新回到設定」&gt;「一般」&gt;「儲存空間與 iCloud 用量」，你會發現可用空間突然神奇的增加了！<br />\n5.接下來，再回到 iTunes Store，重複第 2、第 3 步驟幾次，直到可用空間不再繼續增加為止。"},{"pid":"3a195e2b2c33b8530a9198236ce51f48dd851520","tid":1808543,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d239020787a1978872edb07542aaf6810d5625","tid":1808543,"uid":297236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87bf421b78e9ad6e0b7794c3ddee1ea822e647b1","tid":1808543,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbea13a8295c8c855d6913fdc40354f27ce79033","tid":1808543,"uid":297236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"試咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇咩用<br />\nbtw你仲有咩方法可以減到0.3gb<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求指教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"Offload apps同optimise photo要等一陣<br />\n你再等多陣睇下有冇改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ULd3Zp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ULd3Zp.png&h